quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,The merciful
  55,2,He taught/instructed the Koran
  55,3,He created the human/mankind
  55,4,He taught/instructed him the evidence/logic
  55,5,The sun and the moon with a count/calculation
  55,6,"And the star/planet and the trees, they (B) prostrate"
  55,7,"And the sky/space He rose it, and He laid/put/raised the scale/measuring instrument"
  55,8,That you not tyrannize/exceed the limit in the scale/measuring instrument
  55,9,"And keep up the weight/measure with the just/equitable, and do not reduce/decrease (cheat) in the scale/measuring instrument"
  55,10,"And the earth/Planet Earth, He laid it for the creation"
  55,11,In it (are) fruits and the palm trees that of the buds/covers from which fruits and flowers emerge
  55,12,"And the seed/grain (of) the husk/chaff/external cover of seeds, and the basil/fragrant plants"
  55,13,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,14,He created the human/mankind from dry mud/clay as the pottery/earthenware
  55,15,And He created the Jinn from (the) flaming blazing torch mixed with blackened smoke from fire
  55,16,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,17,"The two sun rises`/easts` Lord, and the two sunsets`/declines` Lord"
  55,18,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,19,"The two large bodies of water usually salty mixed/set loose, they (B) meet"
  55,20,"Between them (B) (is) a barrier , they (B) do not transgress"
  55,21,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,22,The pearls and the corals emerge from them (B)
  55,23,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,24,And for Him (are) the ships/flowing/passing the raised/developed in the sea/ocean as/like the banners/mountains
  55,25,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,26,Each/every who (is) on it (is) vanishing/being destroyed
  55,27,And your Lord`s face/front/direction (owner) of the glory/splendor and the honour/generosity remains/continues
  55,28,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,29,"Who (ever is) in the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth asks/questions him, each/every day/time He is in a great matter/affair/concern"
  55,30,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,31,"We will finish/end/complete (free ourselves) for you, oh you, the humans and Jinns (the two weights)"
  55,32,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,33,"You race/society (of) the Jinns and human/mankind, if you were able that (E) you penetrate/pierce from the skies`/space`s and the earth`s/Planet Earth`s regions/diameters/chords , so penetrate/pierce , you do not penetrate/pierce except with power/ authority"
  55,34,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,35,"He sends on you (B) a smokeless flame/blazing heat from fire and copper/sparks of molten iron , so you (B) do not become victorious"
  55,36,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,37,"So if the sky/space split/cut open , so it was a red/a rose as/like the paint/painted with oil"
  55,38,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,39,"So that day (end of the world till judgment takes place), a human/mankind and nor a Jinn (will) be asked/questioned about his crime"
  55,40,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,41,"The criminals/sinners (will) be known by their marks/identifications/expressions, so (they) will be taken by the foreheads/forehead`s hair (bangs), and the feet"
  55,42,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,43,This is Hell which the criminals/sinners lie/deny with it
  55,44,They circle/walk around between it and between hot water/cold water/red hot coal blazing/glowing
  55,45,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,46,"And to who feared His Lord`s place/position , two treed gardens"
  55,47,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,48,of (the two treed gardens) have branches
  55,49,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,50,"In them (B) (are) two water springs/wells, they (B) flow"
  55,51,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,52,"In them (B) (are) from every/each fruits, a pair/couple/two kinds"
  55,53,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,54,"Leaning/reclining on on spreads/beds its lining/interior (is) from brocade , and the two treed gardens` harvest (fruits is) near"
  55,55,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,56,"In them (B) (are) confining the eyes, (they) were not touched (by) a human before them, and nor Jinn"
  55,57,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,58,"As if/though they (F) are corundum/hardest mineral after diamond (rubies/sapphires/ topazes), and the corals"
  55,59,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,60,"Is the goodness` reimbursement , except the goodness"
  55,61,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,62,And from other than them (B) two treed gardens
  55,63,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,64,(are) blackish green and fragrant
  55,65,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,66,"In them (B) (are) two water springs/wells, (B) flowing/gushing"
  55,67,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,68,"In them (B) (are) fruits, and palm trees, and pomegranate"
  55,69,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,70,In them (B) (are) very beautiful good/generous
  55,71,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,72,Dilated pupils (very beautiful) confined/limited in the tents
  55,73,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,74,"(They) were not touched (by) a human before them, and nor Jinn"
  55,75,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,76,Leaning/relining on green carpets/pillows/silk and very beautiful fine carpets
  55,77,So with which (of) your (B)`s (humans and Jinns) Lord`s blessings (do) you (B) deny/falsify
  55,78,"Blessed (is) your Lord`s name, (owner) of the glory/splendor and the honour/generosity"